Articles.Content:
So I was playing some career recently.

When I was getting the last pieces of science I needed from Eeloo, The sudden Realization came to my mind that Duna was still unexplored.

I took the best software known to Kerbalkind (Open Broadcaster and Movie Maker) and created this video.

And yes, there are about 30 orange tank transfer stages marked as debris flying around Kerbin.

Nice video! There should be more positive comments for your video, but alas, it takes effort to type.

Gravity was not kind to your landing stage...
